          </div>

          <div class="bg-blue-100 border-l-[3px] border-blue-700 pl-6 py-5 rounded-r">
            <p class="text-sm font-black text-blue-800 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">THE AFTER (90 Days Later - June 2023)</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Tour inquiries: 8-12/week to 22-28/week (+180%). Open house attendance: 25-35 families to 65-80 families (+107%). Time-on-site: 1:47 to 4:12 (+143%) because parents actually found curriculum information. Enrollment for next year: first waitlist in school's 12-year history. Parent feedback: "Your website showed me exactly what my child would learn every day." Phone calls asking basic questions: dropped 67% (information was now findable). Annual revenue impact: +$450,000 in tuition from 18 additional families. ROI: 17,308% in first year. Director: "Our website is now our best admissions officer."</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-900 text-white p-6 rounded-lg">
            <p class="text-sm font-black text-blue-300 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">THE 90-DAY BREAKDOWN</p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-blue-400 font-black">DAY 1-14:</span>
                <span>Website live. Curriculum pages created and linked from homepage. Faculty profiles added with photos.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-blue-400 font-black">DAY 15-30:</span>
                <span>First +127% increase in tour inquiries. Parents: "Finally found the curriculum!" Virtual tour most-viewed page.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-blue-400 font-black">DAY 31-60:</span>
                <span>Word-of-mouth in parent community: "Have you seen Westfield's new website?" Open house attendance doubled.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-blue-400 font-black">DAY 61-90:</span>
                <span>First waitlist in 12 years. School at capacity. Planning expansion to meet demand.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE HARD TRUTH: 6 MISTAKES KILLING SCHOOL WEBSITES -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-orange-50">
