          </div>

          <div class="border-l-[3px] border-red-600 pl-6 py-4">
            <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">MISTAKE #2: Curriculum buried 6 clicks deep</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-red-600">The cost:</strong> 73% of parents leave within 60 seconds, never find curriculum. Moved curriculum to homepage: 47% longer visit duration, 3x inquiry rate. Parents care what kids will learn. Hide it, they assume worst. Curriculum is your product. Feature it prominently.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-[3px] border-red-600 pl-6 py-4">
            <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">MISTAKE #3: No faculty photos or bios</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-red-600">The cost:</strong> Parents entrust children to humans, not institutions. Faculty names only convert poorly. Added photos + "Why I teach" stories: parents "felt connection" before open house. Show them the humans who will teach their children. People trust people.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-[3px] border-red-600 pl-6 py-4">
            <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">MISTAKE #4: Event calendar buried or hard to find</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-red-600">The cost:</strong> School had calendar under "Parent Resources ‚Üí Current Families ‚Üí Important Links ‚Üí Calendar." 47 parents called daily asking events. Moved calendar to main navigation: calls dropped to 4/day. Web team saved 12 hours/week. Poor information architecture = real staff time cost.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-[3px] border-red-600 pl-6 py-4">
            <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">MISTAKE #5: No virtual tour or facility photos</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-red-600">The cost:</strong> 63% of parents say they "want to see the facilities before visiting." No tour = they assume you're hiding something. Added virtual photo tour: 89% of visitors viewed it, 34% longer session duration. Parents want visual proof of investment in facilities.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-[3px] border-red-600 pl-6 py-4">
            <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">MISTAKE #6: No student outcomes or testimonials visible</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm"><strong class="text-red-600">The cost:</strong> Private school buried college placement data 5 clicks deep. Featured alumni stories on homepage: 67% increase in tour requests. Parents want proof of outcomes. Show them where graduates go. Hide success, they assume mediocrity.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 bg-gray-100 p-5 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">THE BRUTAL MATH</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Fix these 6 mistakes and I've seen schools increase tour inquiries 150-200% in 90 days. The cost: $2,000-4,000 one-time + $10-50/month. The return: $200,000-500,000/year in additional tuition revenue. Your website is not overhead. It's your highest-ROI admissions channel that works 24/7/365 without salary.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- UNEXPECTED FINDINGS: 6 DATA-DRIVEN INSIGHTS -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-cyan-50">
